    "With 3,368 records, the Wiki dataset achieves a TPR of 84.2% and a TNR of 83.2%.",
    "The Open Q&A dataset, encompassing 4,748 records, shows a TPR of 74.5% and a TNR of 73.0%.",
    "Among the examined datasets, the Reddit dataset stands out with 99,054 records and perfect scores of 100% for both TPR and TNR.",
    "This analysis implies that the model trained on the Reddit dataset accurately identifies ChatGPT-generated and human-generated content.",
    "Furthermore, the Political dataset, consisting of 3,620 records, demonstrates a TPR of 92% and a TNR of 91.5%."
